\id COL - Mbula 
\h Amǝ Kolosi 
\toc3 Kol 
\toc2 Amǝ Kolosi 
\toc1 Amǝ Kolosi 
\mt2 Cauterǝa mala Bulǝs aban ká a ban 
\mt1 AMƏ KOLOSI 
\imt1 Mǝncau 
\im \bk Cauterǝa mala Bulǝs aban ká a ban Amǝ Kolosi \bk* ka, à gilǝì aban ká aban ikǝlisiya mǝnana a Kolosi, ɓe nggea-là a nzali Asiya Mǝkyauwe, mǝnana dǝurǝo mala nzali yi kiɗikì a pǝlǝa 60 AD ka. Ikǝlisiya mǝnia a la man ngga Bulǝs nǝ̀ mǝnni ɗang, Abafǝras na, sǝ acemǝnana nda aɓa nzong-nzali ban mǝnana Bulǝs twalî ɓamúrì nǝ̀ ɗenyi nǝi ka, kǝ tasǝ amǝtúró à kǝ pur Afisu ɓǝà kyan nggam. Yì Abafǝras ka ɓe ɓwamǝgule na amur amǝkwaɗi; à bang cau male kusǝ pas aɓa mǝnia yì cauterǝa ka, sǝ yì ka, à nda atārǝia andǝ Bulǝs a kùrban a bàkú mǝnana à gilǝ mǝnia yì cauterǝa ka. 
\iot Agir mana aɓalǝi ka 
\io1 Makkun\ior 1:1-8\ior* 
\io1 Ɓealǝu mala Kǝrǝsti andǝ túró male\ior 1:9--2:19\ior* 
\io1 Bǝsa yilǝmu aɓa Kǝrǝsti\ior 2:20--4:6\ior* 
\io1 Masǝlǝata cau\ior 4:7-18\ior* 
\c 1  
\s1 Makkun mala Bulǝs 
\p  
\v 1 Mim Bulǝs, mǝnana mǝ nda mǝ'mishan mala Kǝrǝsti Yesu, nǝ kanì mala Ɓakuli ka, mim sǝnǝ mǝ'eam sǝm Timoti, sǝm gilǝ mǝnia yì Cautera ka. 
\p  
\v 2 Aban ká aban aɓwana mala Ɓakuli mǝnana a nggea-là mala amǝ Kolosi, yia amǝ'eamrǝarǝu aɓa Kǝrǝsti mǝnana à dum nǝ mǝsǝcau aban Ɓakuli ka. Tár sǝm Ɓakuli ɓǝ̀ pà wun ɓwamuru andǝ dorǝpwala. 
\s1 Yàwá andǝ hiwi mala Bulǝs 
\p  
\v 3 Aɓa hiwi ma'sǝm ace wun koya pwari ka, sǝm nggǝ pakki Ɓakuli, Tár Mǝtala sǝm Yesu Kǝrǝsti yàwá,  
\v 4 acemǝnana sǝm ongŋǝna cè paɓamuru ma'wun aɓa Kǝrǝsti Yesu andǝ earcearǝu ma'wun aban aɓwana mala Ɓakuli kat.  
\v 5 Mǝno yì paɓamuru andǝ earcearǝu ma'wun ngga, pur aɓa tsǝkɓalǝu ma'wun arǝ agir mǝnana Ɓakuli tsǝka wunì a kùli ka, mǝnana wu okce aɓa mǝsǝcau mala Cau Amsǝban  
\v 6 mana à yinanǝi aban wun ngga. Mǝnia yì Cau Amsǝban ngga, nda ban mǝsǝe a ɓanza kat. Nda ban pusǝ ɓealu a koya ban, kǝ nggaɗi do mala aɓwana kǝla mǝnana nggaɗi do ma'wun, a pwari mǝnana wu tita o sǝ wu bwalta mǝsǝcau amur ɓwamuru mala Ɓakuli ka.  
\v 7 Abafǝras, ɓi'sǝm mǝtúró mǝnana sǝm earkiyi ace raka, nda ɓwa mǝnana nǝ baní sǝ wu kum sǝlǝe amur mǝnia yì ɓwamuru ka. Yì ka, mǝtúró mala Kǝrǝsti na nǝ mǝsǝcau, sǝ nda mǝnana kǝ bwala sǝm túró ace wun ngga.\f + \fr 1:7 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt Kol 4:12; Film 23\ft .\f* 
\v 8 Yì ɗǝm ngga, yi bangŋǝna sǝm cè earcearǝu ma'wun mǝnana Bangŋo Mǝfele pà wun ngga. 
\p  
\v 9 Acemani ka, twal a pwari mǝnana sǝm tita okce wun ngga, sǝm usǝlǝkiyi pàk hiwi ace wun ɗàng. Sǝm nggǝ zǝmbi Ɓakuli ɓǝ̀ pà wun sǝlǝe mala súrǝ̀ gir mǝnana earkiyice kat ka, sǝ ɓǝ̀ pà wun sǝlǝe mala Bangŋo andǝ bwalta kusǝ agir male kat.  
\v 10 Sǝm nggǝ pàk hiwi mǝnia ka ace mǝnana ɓǝ̀ do ma'wun gusǝlǝ Mǝtalabangŋo, ɓǝ̀ pwasǝ bumi a koya njar, nǝ pak koya túró mǝɓoarne. Anggo sǝ wu nǝ̀ nggǝ gulo aɓa súrǝ̀ Ɓakuli pepè.  
\v 11 Sǝm nggǝ pakhiwi ɗǝm ama kusǝ wun ɓǝ̀ candǝ aɓa rǝcandǝa mala gulo male mǝnana karban kat ka. Anggo sǝ wun nǝ̀ kum gandǝrǝu aɓalǝ agirbunda kat nǝ munyi, sǝ wun nǝ̀ lùmsǝ nǝ banɓoarnado.  
\v 12 Ko aya pwari ka wun nǝ̀ nggǝ pakki Tár sǝm Ɓakuli yàwá. Yì na tsǝa sǝ wu duk aɓwana mǝnana wu kārǝ́na wun nǝ̀ kum kāmbe ma'wun aɓa liɓala atà aɓwana male mǝnana à do aɓa tǎlaban ngga.  
\v 13 Acemǝnana amsǝna sǝm aɓata parban mala Shetan,\f + \fr 1:13 \fq amsǝna sǝm aɓata parban mala Shetan \ft Ko: amsǝna sǝm, sǝm purni rǝcandǝa mala pǝndǝa.\f* sǝ yina nǝ sǝm aɓa Domurǝm mala Muni mǝnana earkiyi ace raka,  
\v 14 mǝnana akmúr sǝm sǝ twalban acauɓikea ma'sǝm ngga.\f + \fr 1:14 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt Afi 1:7,8\ft .\f* 
\s1 Kǝrǝsti gulo karban kat 
\p  
\v 15 Kǝrǝsti ka nda ɓwa mǝnana à kǝ sǝni, mana lǝmdǝ Ɓakuli mǝnana à kǝ sǝni raka. Kaniama Ɓakuli nǝ̀ pusǝ agirbunda kat ka, yì ka, ndakam atà Ɓakuli kǝla Muna-dǝmba male, sǝ ndanǝ gulo kàrmúr agir mǝnana kat Ɓakuli pusǝia ka.  
\v 16 Nǝ baní sǝ Ɓakuli pusǝ koya gìr mǝnana a kùli andǝa mǝnana a nzali ka. Yì nǝ̀ pusǝ agir mǝnana à kǝ sǝnia andǝa mǝnana à kǝ sǝnia raka; kat andǝ abuno-murǝm, andǝ adomurǝm, andǝ amǝ'talanzali, andǝ amǝ bwal gara-murǝm. Nǝ yi sǝ à pusǝ koya gìr ka, sǝ àkǝ̀ cè gulo male sǝ à pusǝia.  
\v 17 Kaniama à nǝ̀ pusǝ koya gìr ka ndakam, sǝ yì nǝ̀ bwal agir mǝnana à pusǝia ka a banɓwáná.  
\v 18 Kǝrǝsti ɗǝm ngga nda múr amǝkpate, yia amǝnana à nda ka nggūrǝì ka. Yì ka, nda tǝr bǝsa yilǝmu mala amǝkpate. Yì nda mǝdǝmba loapi ɓembe, ace mǝnana aɓa ko man kat ka ɓǝ̀ do nda mǝnana a dǝmba amur agir kat ka.\f + \fr 1:18 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt Afi 1:22,23; 4:15\ft .\f* 
\v 19 Acemani ka, Ɓakuli aɓa pa male kat ka, banɓoari wi ɓǝ̀ lǝmdǝ rǝì aɓa Muni,\f + \fr 1:19 \ft Ko: \fqa Ɓakuli ka eare male na ɓǝ̀ nying pa male kat kǝla Ɓakuli ɓǝ̀ do aɓa Muni. \f* 
\v 20 sǝ nǝ ban Muni ka ɓǝ̀ gilǝki tàrǝu mala agirbunda kat andǝi. Nǝ nkila mala Muni mǝnana sukki amur nggun-gangndǝi ka, yina nǝ dorǝpwala, ace mǝnana agir mana kat a kùli andǝa mǝnana a nzali ka, à nǝ̀ nyesǝia aban Ɓakuli.\f + \fr 1:20 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt Afi 2:16\ft .\f* 
\p  
\v 21 Ɗiɗyal ka wu cambi Ɓakuli zak. Wu duk aɓiubura mala Ɓakuli aɓalǝ aɗenyicau ma'wun, mana wu lǝmdǝí nǝ atúró ɓealɓikea ma'wun ngga.  
\v 22 Sǝ adyan ngga, Ɓakuli nyesǝna wun aɓa dotarǝu andǝi, nǝ lú mala Kǝrǝsti aɓa nggūrǝì mala ɓwapǝndǝa. Nyesǝ wun ace mǝnana ɓǝ̀ pǝlǝ wun, ɓǝ̀ wu duk aɓwana ace Ɓakuli, amǝ ɗwanyicau-arǝǔ a sǝne male,\f + \fr 1:22 \fq ace mǝnana ɓǝ̀ pǝlǝ wun, ɓǝ̀ wu duk aɓwana ace Ɓakuli, amǝ ɗwanyicau-arǝǔ a sǝne male \ft Ko: <<sǝ earǝ́nà wun ɓǝ̀ wu came a ɓadǝmbi kǝla aɓwana male, amǝ ɗwanyicau-arǝǔ.>>\f* aɓwana mǝnana à pà nǝ̀ tsǝkia wia kún raka.  
\v 23 Sǝama dumǝna púp wun nǝ̀ lidǝmba nǝ earnǝ mǝno yì mǝsǝcau ka, andǝ tamsǝ kusǝ wun kàngkàng amurí. Wu kǝa tusǝ kusǝ wun arǝ tsǝkɓalǝu mǝnana wu oè aɓa Cau Amsǝban ngga ɗàng. Mǝnia yì Cau Amsǝban ngga à hamǝna nǝi a koya bum-ban a ɓanza, sǝ àkǝ̀ cè sǝ mim Bulǝs ka, ǝn duk guro mala Ɓakuli, ace hamnǝi. 
\s1 Túró mala Bulǝs ace amǝkpata Yesu 
\p  
\v 24 Sǝ ado ka ban kǝ ɓoaram arǝ tanni mǝnana ǝn nggǝ nu ace wun ngga. Acemǝnana aɓa tanni mem a nggūrǝu ka, mǝ nda ban ɓariki mǝ lùmsǝkún gir mǝnana ueo aɓa tanni mala Kǝrǝsti ace nggūrǝì, yì amǝkpate.  
\v 25 Ɓakuli tsǝngŋǝnami a buam ɓǝ̀n pakki ikǝlisiya, yia amǝkpata Yesu túró, mǝ nggǝ hamnǝ cau male kat aban wun.  
\v 26 Mǝnia yì cau ka à sǝmbǝrǝce arǝ apǝlǝa ɓara-ɓara andǝ anza mǝno à kutikina ka, sǝ adyan ngga à pusǝni aban aɓwana mala Ɓakuli, ɓǝà sǝlǝce.  
\v 27 Ɓakuli earnace ɓǝ̀ aɓwana male sǝlǝce gulo andǝ kume mana aɓa mǝnia yì cau-ɓa-sǝmbǝrǝa, mǝnana ndanǝi ace aɓwana mana amǝ Yahudi na raka.\f + \fr 1:27 \fq aɓwana mana amǝ Yahudi na raka. \ft Ko: aɓwapǝndǝa mala anzali ɓanza ka.\f* Sǝ mǝnia yì cau-ɓa-sǝmbǝrǝa ka nda mǝnana ama: Kǝrǝsti mǝnana do aɓalǝ wun ngga, nda tsǝkɓalǝu ma'wun mala kum kāmbe aɓa gulo mala Ɓakuli. 
\p  
\v 28 Nda gìrnî sǝ sǝm nggǝ banggi aɓwana cau mala Kǝrǝsti, sǝm nggǝ nunkir koyan ngga. Sǝm nggǝ kani koyan ngga nǝ sǝlǝe mǝnana kat Ɓakuli pa sǝm ngga. Sǝm nggǝ earce ama sǝm nǝ̀ yinǝia a ɓadǝm Ɓakuli kǝla aɓwana mǝnana à lùmsǝ̀nà aɓa do malea andǝ Kǝrǝsti ka.  
\v 29 Acemani ka ǝn nggǝ paktúró, ǝn nggǝ ɓariki kǝ̀rkǝ́r, nǝ gūlì arǝ rǝcandǝa mǝgule mala Kǝrǝsti mǝnana pàkkiyi túró aɓalǝam ngga. 
\c 2  
\p  
\v 1 Ən nggǝ earce ɓǝ̀ wu súrǝ̀ ulang tanni mǝnana ǝn nggǝ tanni ace wun, andǝ amǝkpata Yesu mǝnana a Lawodisi, andǝ amǝkpata Yesu mǝnana kat à malaká sǝnam à súrǝàm raka.  
\v 2 Ən nggǝ pak mǝnia ace mǝnana ɓǝà kum ɓakɓabum, sǝ ɓǝà duk mwashat aɓa earcearǝu. Ən nggǝ earce nǝma ɓǝà kum lùmsǝo mala ɓabumcandǝa ama à bwalǝnata kàné mala Ɓakuli mana sǝmbǝrǝce ɗiɗyal ka, yì Kǝrǝsti nǝ ɓamúrì.  
\v 3 Aɓa Kǝrǝsti sǝ gǝna mala sǝlǝe andǝ súrǝè mala Ɓakuli kat sǝmbǝrǝa.  
\v 4 Ən nggǝ na wun mǝnia yì cau ka ace mǝnana kǝɓwa ɓǝ̀ kǝa swarki wun nǝ kunɓoarna ɗang.  
\v 5 Ko ɓǝ̀ do ama ǝn pa atà wun aɓa nggūrǝu raka, mǝ nda atà wun aɓa bangŋo. Sǝ ban kǝ ɓoaram arǝ gya a tàrǝu ma'wun, andǝ came mala paɓamuru ma'wun nǝ rǝcandǝa aban Kǝrǝsti. 
\s1 Kum-ɓamuru andǝ bǝsa  //  yilǝmu aɓa Kǝrǝsti 
\p  
\v 6 Sǝ adyan ngga, kǝla mǝnana wu angŋǝna Kǝrǝsti Yesu, dumǝna mǝtala wun ngga, wu lidǝmba nǝ kpate.  
\v 7 Nlerǝ wun ɓǝ̀ ko aɓa Kǝrǝsti, sǝ ɓǝ̀ duk kusǝɓa mala do ma'wun. Ɓǝ̀ paɓamuru ma'wun kum rǝcandǝa kǝla mǝnana à kania wun ngga, sǝ wu lùmsǝ nǝ pak yàwá. 
\p  
\v 8 Wu kǝa eari kǝɓwa ɓǝ̀ swarki wun nǝ amakgìr amur súrǝè male mǝlime mana ɓekǝ mǝɓoarne pà kàm aɓalǝi raka. Ulang mǝno yì amakgìr ka à kǝ pur aɓa kanigir mana à kumi a bu ɓwapǝndǝa, andǝ abangŋo mala ɓanza man, mǝnana mala Kǝrǝsti na raka.  
\v 9 Acemǝnana lùmsǝo mala Ɓakuli kat aɓa nggūrǝu ka, aɓa Kǝrǝsti sǝ pa.  
\v 10 Sǝ wun gbal ka, wu lùmsǝ̀nà ace dotarǝu ma'wun wunǝa Kǝrǝsti, yì ɓwa mǝnana nda amur amǝ'yálmúrû andǝ amǝ-gara kat ka.  
\v 11 Kǝrǝsti gbal ka twalǝna wun ɓealu mala cauɓikea, kǝla mǝnana kasǝ-ɓatau pusǝ nggū arǝ nggūrǝu ka.  
\v 12 Wun ngga, à oasǝna wun a ɓembe wunǝa Kǝrǝsti nǝ batisǝma mǝnana à pakka wun ngga, sǝ aɓa batisǝma ɗǝm ngga à loasǝna wun aɓa bǝsa yilǝmu, nǝ gūlì ma'wun arǝ rǝcandǝa mala Ɓakuli mǝnana loasǝ Kǝrǝsti a ɓembe ka.\f + \fr 2:12 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt Rom 6:4\ft .\f* 
\p  
\v 13 Ɗiɗyal ka, wu wú atàcau mala acauɓikea ma'wun, andǝ aɓealu mala cauɓikea ma'wun mǝnana à gau wun wunǝia raka.\f + \fr 2:13 \fq Ɗiɗyal ka, wu wú atàcau mala acauɓikea ma'wun, andǝ aɓealu mala cauɓikea ma'wun mǝnana à gau wun wunǝia raka. \ft Ko: <<Ɗiɗyal ka, wu nda ka lú acemǝnana wu nda aɓalǝ acauɓikea, sǝ wu nda ka ɓwana mala Ɓakuli ɗang.>>\f* Sǝ adyan ngga Ɓakuli pana wun yilǝmu aɓa Kǝrǝsti, lang yi twala sǝm ban acauɓikea ma'sǝm kat ka.\f + \fr 2:13 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt Afi 2:1-5\ft .\f* 
\v 14 Yi panzǝki ɓashi mǝnana à gilǝì amur sǝm ngga; yi kasǝki kat andǝ anzongcau mala nggurcau mǝnana à bwal sǝm nǝi ka; twalia umnǝia kya gbàllia a nggun-gangndǝi.\f + \fr 2:14 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt Afi 2:15\ft .\f* 
\v 15 Yi ak agirbura mala amurǝma andǝ arǝcandǝa mala abangŋo. Pea wia kǝsǝkya a banfana bwāng, nǝ limurǝm male amúrià amur nggun-gangndǝi. 
\p  
\v 16 Acemani ka, wu kǝa eari kǝɓwa ɓǝ̀ tsǝka wun nzongcau amur agir mǝnana wun nǝ̀ li ko wun nǝ̀ nu ka, ko amur cau mala pakki alamsan mala aɓea kunacau, ko mala came mala bǝsa zongŋo, ko mala Pwari Sabbat ɗang.\f + \fr 2:16 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt Rom 14:1-6\ft .\f* 
\v 17 Amǝnia yì agir ka, ayilǝmi agir mǝɓafoe mǝnana à nda rǝ yiu ka nda. Sǝ Kǝrǝsti nǝ nggearǝì ka nda kǝ ɓafoe.  
\v 18 Wu kǝa eare ɓǝ̀ kǝ ɓwa mǝ'earce pàkkiagir nyesǝmuru mǝ'nyirì\f + \fr 2:18 \fq mǝ'earce pàkkiagir nyesǝmuru mǝ'nyirì: \ft Ko <<ɓwa mǝnana cam kingging nǝ kanigir ama ɓwa nǝ̀ kum nyesǝmuru nǝ ɓinǝì ɓamúrì do aɓa ɓǝlkya andǝ banɓoarnado ka.>>\f* andǝ mǝperi aban amǝturonjar nyesǝce wun ɓà\f + \fr 2:18 \ft Ko \fqa <<Wu būrǝce aɓwana mǝnana à kǝ na wun ama Ɓakuli nǝ̀ ɓasha wun ace mǝnana wu kǝ kpata pàkkiagir malea mala nyesǝmuru mǝ'nyirì andǝ peri aban amǝturonjar raka.>>\f* nǝ nacau gula ama sǝna na sǝn amur amǝnia yì agir ka ɗang. Acau mala ɓwa kǝla mǝno ka amǝɓane na, acemǝnana yì ka, lùmsǝ nǝ twàlɓamúrû, sǝ ɗenyicau male ka, mala earce gìr mala ɓamúrì na.  
\v 19 Mǝnia yì ɓwa ka pa ɗǝm aɓa kpapi andǝ Kǝrǝsti, mǝnana nda mur nggūrǝu kat, yia amǝkpata Yesu ka ɗang. Acemǝnana Kǝrǝsti ka nda kùr múr amǝkpate a banɓwáná, kǝla mǝnana mazo kpakǝri amú ka. Kǝ linǝia, à kǝ gulo aɓa rǝcandǝa mala Ɓakuli.\f + \fr 2:19 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt Afi 4:16\ft .\f* 
\p  
\v 20 Wun ngga, wu wuna wunǝa Kǝrǝsti sǝ à panzǝna wun a bu rǝcandǝa mala abangŋo mala mǝnia yì ɓanza ka. Sǝ ace mana sǝ wu kǝ dukdo kǝla weama wu nda ka mala ɓanza ka? Man tsǝa sǝ wu kǝ kpata anzongcau mala amǝɓanza mǝnana ama:  
\v 21 <<Kǝa bwal man ɗang. Kǝa ok mǝno a lasǝo ɗàng. Kǝa je amǝnia ka ɗang?>>  
\v 22 A'ulang amǝnia yì anggurcau ka, kǝ akanìgìr mala ɓwapǝndǝa na amur agir mǝnana, aɓa pak túró nǝia ka, à pà nǝ̀ sau ɗang à nǝ̀ kiɗiki ka.  
\v 23 A'ulang anggurcau man ngga à lǝmdǝa kǝla sǝlǝe na aɓalǝia, acemǝnana à kǝ earce ama ɓwa ɓǝ̀ oasǝ ɓamúrì aɓalǝia ɓǝ̀ peri aban amǝturonjar, ɓǝ̀ ɓinǝì ɓamúrì do aɓa ɓǝlkya andǝ banɓoarnado, sǝ ɓǝ̀ pe nggūrǝì tanni. Sǝa ma amǝno ka à pà nǝ̀ tsǝk ɓwa nǝ̀ limurǝm amur asuno mǝɓane mala nggūrǝì ɗang. 
\c 3  
\s1 Do bǝsa yilǝmu 
\p  
\v 1 Acemǝnana à loasǝna wun nǝ bǝsa yilǝmu aɓa Kǝrǝsti ka, wu tsǝk ɓabum wun arǝ agir mǝnana a kùli, aban mǝnana Kǝrǝsti dukam abuno gulo a bù-mǝlì mala Ɓakuli ka.  
\v 2 Ɓǝ̀ ɗenyicau ma'wun ɓǝ̀ o amur agir mǝnana a kùli ka, ɓǝ̀ kǝa nyare amur agir mǝnana a nzali ka ɗang.  
\v 3 Acemǝnana wun ngga, wu wunî doɓanza man, sǝ mǝsǝrǝ yilǝmi wun ngga à sǝmbǝrǝni atà Kǝrǝsti aban Ɓakuli.  
\v 4 Sǝ ɓǝ̀ Kǝrǝsti mǝnana nda tǝr bǝsa yilǝmu ma'wun, yi pusǝna rǝì aban ɓanza kat ka, wun gbal ka wu nǝ̀ yia pusǝ rǝ wun aɓa gulo male. 
\p  
\v 5 Ace mani ka, wu wal-lú koya ɓeal wun mala pakki agirɓana mala ɓanza. Yì aɓealu kìɗìkì mala nongginǝ rǝarǝu, andǝ do-pǝndǝkya, andǝ nshawari, andǝ suno mǝɓane, andǝ shamgir mala ɓwa (acemǝnana shamgir mala ɓwa ka ɓè njar mala peri atà nkul na).  
\v 6 Ace amǝnia yì acauɓikea ka sǝ bumlulla mala Ɓakuli nǝ̀ yia sulǝo amur amǝ'murcandǝa.  
\v 7 Aɓa do ma'wun mala gyata ɓanza ɗiɗyal ka wu pakkina amǝnia yì agir ka.  
\v 8 Sǝ adyan ngga dumǝna púp wu nǝ̀ bwaki bu wun arǝ agir kǝla amǝnia ka: bumlulla, sǝ bumkpǝmna, sǝ ɓwashiriɓe, sǝ nacau kiɗiki ɓwa, andǝ naki acauɓana.  
\v 9 Wu kǝa nea rǝ wun nyir ɗang, acemǝnana wu swárǝna ɓeal wun mǝ'e andǝ atúró ɓealɓikea male\f + \fr 3:9 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt Afi 4:22\ft .\f* 
\v 10 sǝ wu twalǝna ɓealu mala bǝsa ɓwa. Mǝnia ka nda bǝsa ɓealu, mana Ɓakuli pusǝì ka. Yì ka nda rǝ pak túró nǝ̀ tsǝk mǝnia yì bǝsa ɓealu ma'wun ngga ɓǝ̀ lidǝmba nǝ pǝlǝ bǝshe a koya pwari, ace ká twal ulang male yì ɓealu, ace mǝnana ɓǝ̀ wu súrǝì pepè ka.\f + \fr 3:10 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt Tite 1:26; Afi 4:24\ft .\f* 
\v 11 Aɓa mǝnia yì bǝsa yilǝmu ka, gakitacau pà kàm ɗǝm ɗàng ama mǝnia ka ɓwa Yahudi na, sǝ mǝnia ka ɓwa ɓe nzali na, mǝnia ka kasǝ ɓate, sǝ mǝnia ka kasǝ ɓate ɗàng. Kǝ cau pà kàm ɗǝm ama mǝnia ka súrǝ̀gir ɗàng, ko mǝnia ka ɓwa kúnɗàngna na, ko man ngga guro na, ko mǝno ka ndanǝ do-ɓamuri ka ɗàng. Kǝrǝsti ka nda komana le ka, sǝ nda mǝnana do a ɓabum sǝm kat ka. 
\p  
\v 12 \f + \fr 3:12 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt Afi 4:2\ft .\f*Sǝ acemǝnana Ɓakuli tarnà wun ɓǝ̀ wu duk aɓwana male mǝnana kǝ earcea ka, wu twal ɓealu mala sǝn mǝsǝswatǝr, andǝ pěmǝɓoarne, andǝ nyesǝɓamuru, andǝ doɓuɓɓuka, sǝ munyi.  
\v 13 Wu kǝ twalban aɓwarkio mala rǝarǝ wun nǝ gandǝrǝu, sǝ wu kǝ twali koyana mǝnana pakka wun mǝɓane ka banì. Wu ɗenyi ama Mǝtalabangŋo twala wun banì, sǝ ace mani ka dumǝna wun púp wun nǝ̀ twalia rǝ wun banì.\f + \fr 3:13 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt Afi 4:32\ft .\f* 
\v 14 Sǝ mǝnana kàrmuria kat ka nda, wu lùmsǝ nǝ earcearǝu, acemǝnana earcearǝu na kùr komana kat ka arǝarǝia aɓa lùmsǝo mala dotarǝu mǝɓoarne. 
\p  
\v 15 Sǝ wu nying dorǝpwala mǝnana pur nǝban Kǝrǝsti ka, ɓǝ̀ ak ɓabum wun. Acemǝnana kǝla nggūrǝu mǝ'mwashati ka, à tunǝ wun ace dorǝpwala. Koya pwari ka wu kǝ pak yàwá.  
\v 16 Ɓǝ̀ cau mala Kǝrǝsti, nǝ ɓoaro male kat ka, lùmsǝ ɗenyicau ma'wun. Wu kǝ kania rǝ wun gir sǝ wu kwarkir rǝarǝ wun, nǝ sǝlǝe mǝnana kat Kǝrǝsti pa sǝm ngga. Wu kǝ tuka anggyal ɓwangsǝ Ɓakuli, andǝ anggyal gusǝlǝ Ɓakuli, andǝ anggyal ɓak aɓwana aɓa bangŋo, nǝ ɓabum pak yàwá aban Ɓakuli.\f + \fr 3:16 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt Afi 5:19,20\ft .\f* 
\v 17 Sǝ ɓǝ̀ mana kat wun nǝ̀ pa, ko wun nǝ̀ na ka, wu pè nǝ ɗenyicau ama wu nda ban pe kǝla amǝ'nakún Mǝtalabangŋo Yesu, wu kǝ pakki Tár sǝm Ɓakuli yàwá nǝ bani yì Kǝrǝsti. 
\s1 Anzongcau ace doɓala  //  mala amǝkwaɗi 
\p  
\v 18 Wun amā-ɓala ka, wu nyesǝ mur wun aɓata abura wun, kǝla mǝnana ɓoaro amǝkwaɗi Mǝtalabangŋo ɓǝa pak ka.\f + \fr 3:18 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt Afi 5:22; 1Bit 3:1\ft .\f* 
\p  
\v 19 Wun aburana, wu earce amālá wun, wu kǝa wu pekia ɗang.\f + \fr 3:19 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt Afi 5:25; 1Bit 3:7\ft .\f* 
\p  
\v 20 Wun amuna ka, wu okî amǝɓǝl wun, acemǝnana mǝnia ka kǝ pwasǝbum Mǝtalabangŋo.\f + \fr 3:20 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt Afi 6:1\ft .\f* 
\p  
\v 21 Wun atárrú, wu kǝa wu soaki ɓabum amuna wun ɗang, ɓǝa a na raka wu nǝ̀ ɓungi ɓabumia.\f + \fr 3:21 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt Afi 6:4\ft .\f* 
\p  
\v 22 \f + \fr 3:22 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt Afi 6:5-8\ft .\f*Wun aguro ka, wu okî amǝtala-ɓala ma'wun a ɓanza aɓa koya gir wu nǝ̀ pak kat ka. Wu ɓariki wu pak túró mǝnana nǝ̀ pwasǝ bumia koya pwari ka. Wu kǝa pe acemǝnana à nda ban sǝn wun ngga ɗang, wu pakkia wia túró nǝ ɓabum mwashat ace pagulo aban andǝ ɓanggi Mǝtalabangŋo.  
\v 23 Ɓǝ̀ mana wu pakkiyi ka, wu pak túrè nǝ ɓabum wun kat kǝla Mǝtalabangŋo na wu pakkiyi wi ka, ɓwapǝndǝa na ɗang.  
\v 24 Wu kǝ ɗenyi ama tangnakusǝu mǝnana Mǝtalabangŋo nǝ̀ pa wun ngga nda liɓala, sǝ mǝtala-ɓala mǝnana wu pakkiyi wi túró ka, Kǝrǝsti na.  
\v 25 Sǝ ɓǝ̀ wu kǝ pak túró ɓealɓikea ka, à nǝ̀ mbwe wun nǝ tangnakusǝu mǝkwanbanì. Acemǝnana ɓashi mala Ɓakuli aban aɓwana kat ka, mǝ'mwashati na\f + \fr 3:25 \fqa Ko: <<Ɓakuli ka kǝ lǝmdǝ tàrban ɗang.>>\f*.\f + \fr 3:25 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt Nggur 10:17; Afi 6:9\ft .\f* 
\c 4  
\s1 Akwarkiru 
\p  
\v 1 Wun amǝtala-ɓala, wu bwal aguro ma'wun nǝ mǝsǝcau, wu kǝ pakkia wia mǝɓoarne. Wu ɗenyi ama wun gbal ka wu ndanǝ mǝtala-ɓala akanó a kùli.\f + \fr 4:1 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt Afi 6:9\ft .\f* 
\p  
\v 2 Wu pa ɓamur rǝ wun arǝ pak hiwi, sǝ aɓa pe ka wu dum nǝ kwaro mala dǝmbu andǝ ɓabum mala pak yàwá aban Ɓakuli.  
\v 3 Wu pakka sǝm hiwi gbal ama ɓǝ̀ Ɓakuli pa sǝm dǝmbǝu mala bang cau male, ɓǝ̀ sǝm hamnǝ cau-ɓa-sǝmbǝrǝa male mǝnana amur Kǝrǝsti ka. Àkǝ̀ ce mǝnia yì cau ka, sǝ mǝ nda a ndàkurban ado.  
\v 4 Wu pak hiwi ama, mǝ hamnǝ mǝnia yì cau ka puret-puret, kǝla mǝnana ɓoaro mǝ hamnǝi ka. 
\p  
\v 5 Wu dum nǝ kwaro a do ma'wun aɓalǝ aɓwana mǝnana à ak Cau Amsǝban raka, sǝ koya dǝmbǝu mǝnana wu kum ngga, wu kǝa kiɗiki ce ɓà ɗang.\f + \fr 4:5 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt Afi 5:16\ft .\f* 
\v 6 Cau mǝnana nǝ̀ puro a kun wun ngga, ɓǝ̀ pa aɓa ɓuɓɓuka mala ɗenyi nǝ ɓwa, sǝ ɓǝ̀ ɓoari ɓwapǝndǝa o, ace mǝnana anggo sǝ wu nǝ̀ súrǝ̀ lang sǝ wu nǝ̀ pǝlǝi koyan ngga cau, mana ɓǝa ɗì wun ngga. 
\s1 Masǝlǝata akwarkiru andǝ  //  amakkun mala Bulǝs 
\p  
\v 7 Gyajam mǝɓoarne ma'sǝm Tikikus nǝ̀ bǝla wun ce gìr mǝnana mǝ nda aɓalǝi ka kat. Yì ka, mǝ'eamrǝarǝu mǝɓafoe na aɓa túró, ɓwa na mǝnana à nǝ̀ gūlì arǝì ka, sǝ ɓi'sǝm guro na aɓa túró mala Mǝtalabangŋo.\f + \fr 4:7 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt Atúró 20:4; Afi 6:21-22; 2Tim 4:12\ft .\f* 
\v 8 Ən tasǝi aban wun, ace mǝnana ɓǝ̀ na wun gìr mǝnana sǝm nggǝ pak kani ka, sǝ ɓǝ̀ ɓak ɓabum wun.  
\v 9 Ndya ɗǝm ǝn nggǝ tasǝ Onisǝmu ka. Yì gbal ka, mǝ'eamrǝarǝu mǝɓafoe na mǝnana à nǝ̀ gūlì arǝì ka, nggearǝ yì ka, kǝ ɓwa ma'wun na. Yì andǝ Tikikus ka à nǝ̀ bangga wun gìr mǝnana kat kǝ kumban kani ka.\f + \fr 4:9 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt Film 10-12\ft .\f* 
\p  
\v 10 Aristakus mǝnana nda kani atàm a ndàkurban ngga, kǝ makka wun kun, anggo gbal sǝ Markus mǝnana kèa mwashat andǝ Barnabas ka, kǝ makka wun kun. Kǝla mǝnana à bangŋǝna wun cau amurí yì Markus ka, ɓǝ̀ yina ka wu gingsǝi caca.\f + \fr 4:10 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt Atúró 12:12,25; 13:13; 15:37-39; 19:29; 27:2; Film 24\ft .\f* 
\v 11 Yesu mǝnana à tunǝki ama Yustus ka, kǝ makka wun kún gbal. Kǝ amǝnia yì aburana ka, à nda ka amǝ Yahudi aɓalǝ aɓeam amǝtúró ace Domurǝm mala Ɓakuli. À ɓak ɓabumam nǝ rǝcandǝa. 
\p  
\v 12 Abafǝras, mǝnana ɓi'wun na aɓa dotarǝu mala amǝ'eamrǝarǝu a akana aban wun, sǝ ɗǝm ngga guro mala Kǝrǝsti Yesu na ka, kǝ makka wun kún. Ko aya pwari ka kǝ pak hiwi ace wun nǝ mǝsǝcau, kǝ zǝmbi Ɓakuli ɓǝ̀ pa wun rǝcandǝa, sǝ ɓǝ̀ wu lùmsǝ nǝ mǝsǝkang-kangŋa, mǝnana wu nǝ̀ nggǝ kpata kani mala Ɓakuli kat ka.\f + \fr 4:12 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt Kol 1:7; Film 23\ft .\f* 
\v 13 Mǝ nǝ gandǝ na kúni ama kǝ pak túró kǝ̀rkǝ́r ace wun, sǝ ace amǝkwaɗi mǝnana a Lawodisi andǝ Herapoli ka. 
\p  
\v 14 Luka, mǝsonzǝo mǝnana sǝm earkiyi ace raka, andǝ Dimas, à kǝ makka wun kún.\f + \fr 4:14 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt 2Tim 4:10,11; Film 24\ft .\f* 
\p  
\v 15 Wu pa makkun mem aban amǝ'eamrǝarǝu mǝnana a Lawodisi ka, nggeamurǝmi ka mǝ'nggaula sǝm Nimfa, andǝ amǝkpata Yesu mǝnana à kǝ dapi a ɓala male ka. 
\p  
\v 16 Anzǝm mǝnana wu ɓalna mǝnia yì cauterǝa ka, wu tasǝia amǝkpata Yesu mǝnana a Lawodisi ka ɓǝa ɓalli gbal. Sǝ wun gbal ka wu ɓal malea mǝnana ǝn gilǝia wia ka. 
\p  
\v 17 Sǝ wu banggi Arkipus mǝnia yì cau ka: <<Tsǝkiro arǝ túró mǝnana Mǝtalabangŋo po ka, masǝlǝte.>>\f + \fr 4:17 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt Film 2\ft .\f* 
\p  
\v 18 Mim Bulǝs, mǝ nda ǝn gilǝ mǝnia yì makkun ngga nǝ buam. 
\p Wu ɗenyi ama mǝ nda a ndàkurban. 
\p Ɓwamuru mala Ɓakuli ɓǝ̀ do atà wun.